WEBVTT

00:00,000 --> 00:04,950
Most teams blame tools for weak playbook results, but execution discipline is the real gap.

00:05,000 --> 00:09,950
Without a clear review habit, practical quality drifts even when effort increases. Most teams do not...

00:10,000 --> 00:14,950
Pick one owner and one metric, then run one weekly checkpoint in the workstream.

00:15,000 --> 00:19,950
Run a one-week pilot, capture evidence from real behavior, then adjust immediately.

00:20,000 --> 00:24,950
That pattern raises first-pass quality, strengthens weekly review quality, and reduces avoidable rework.

00:25,000 --> 00:29,950
What is the first review loop you can install this week?
